Built on [pyarnes](https://github.com/Cognitivemesh/pyarnes) — an agentic harness engineering template.

## What you get from pyarnes

| Package | What it provides |
|---|---|
| `pyarnes_core` | Types (`ToolHandler`, `ModelClient`), four-error taxonomy, lifecycle FSM, JSONL logging |
| `pyarnes_harness` | `AgentLoop`, `ToolRegistry`, output capture, tool-call logger |
| `pyarnes_guardrails` | `PathGuardrail`, `CommandGuardrail`, `GuardrailChain` |
| `pyarnes_bench` | Evaluation scoring framework |
| `pyarnes_tasks` | The `tasks` CLI |

